---
<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 py-14 md:py-20 grid md:grid-cols-[11fr_9fr] gap-10 items-center">
  <div>
    <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-[var(--color-accent)] mb-4">
      Strategy, execution, support
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold leading-[1.15] mb-6">
      Marketing strategy, execution, and support
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-[var(--color-slate)] max-w-md mb-10">
      We partner with ambitious organizations to plan with clarity, execute with precision, and grow with confidence.
    </p>
    <a
      href="/contact"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-4 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--color-paper)] border border-[var(--color-line)] px-8 py-5 text-lg text-[var(--color-ink)] hover:border-[var(--color-slate)] transition-colors"
    >
      <span
        class="w-9 h-9 rounded-full shrink-0 ring-2 ring-white"
        style="background: radial-gradient(circle at 35% 30%, #f2789a 0%, var(--color-accent) 60%, #c72f5e 100%); box-shadow: 0 0 14px 3px rgba(232, 70, 124, 0.5);"
      ></span>
      How can we help?
    </a>
  </div>
  <div class="hidden md:block">
    <img
      src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/vandalist-hero.png`}
      alt="Abstract still life of strategy pieces: a pink X, an engraved play-diagram panel, an arch, a sphere, and a bowl with a pink sphere"
      class="w-full h-auto"
    />
  </div>
</div>
